question.en:
Consider this ES6 class inheritance scenario. What is logged?
```js
class Animal {
  constructor(name) {
    this.name = name;
  }
}
class Dog extends Animal {
  constructor(name, breed) {
    super(name);
    this.breed = breed;
  }
}
const dog = new Dog('Rex', 'Labrador');
console.log(dog instanceof Dog, dog instanceof Animal, dog instanceof Object);
```

